# Sample Excel Data for Member Import

## 📋 **REQUIRED COLUMNS**
- **fileno** OR **employeeno** (Member ID - at least one required)
- **surname** (Last name - required)
- **firstname** (First name - required)

## 📊 **SAMPLE DATA**

| societycode | instcode | fileno | surname | firstname | middlename | gender | email | teleno | bankcode | openbal |
|-------------|----------|----------|----------|------------|------------|--------|--------|---------|----------|----------|
| SOC001 | BR001 | STU2024001 | Smith | John | Doe | M | john.smith@email.com | 08012345678 | BANK001 | 5000.00 |
| SOC001 | BR001 | STU2024002 | Johnson | Mary | Jane | F | mary.j@email.com | 08087654321 | BANK001 | 3000.00 |
| SOC001 | BR002 | STU2024003 | Williams | Robert | | M | robert.w@email.com | 08098765432 | BANK002 | 7500.50 |
| SOC002 | BR001 | TEA2024001 | Brown | Sarah | Elizabeth | F | sarah.brown@email.com | 08056789012 | BANK001 | 2000.00 |

## 📝 **ADDITIONAL COLUMNS (Optional)**

| presaddress | permaddress | depcode | kinname | kinaddress | kinteleno | kinrelation | maritalstatus | bankaccno |
|-------------|-------------|---------|----------|------------|-----------|-------------|---------------|-----------|
| 123 Main St | 123 Main St | DEPT001 | John Smith Sr | 123 Main St | 08012345679 | Father | Single | 1234567890 |
| 456 Oak Ave | 456 Oak Ave | DEPT002 | Mary Johnson Sr | 456 Oak Ave | 08087654322 | Mother | Married | 2345678901 |
